{"tid":985325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Fake News] 消委會運動手帶測試 ，南華早報SCMP 刻意隱藏報導小米嚴重偏差則","createTime":"2019-01-17T13:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T12:17:36.000Z","uid":28195,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e867c86ae73694655bd1a383f945ef9bef0fa0","tid":985325,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:16:09.000Z","msg":"<strong>SCMP: </strong>Smartwatches and fitness bands by Suunto, Apple and Garmin can be inaccurate, Hong Kong Consumer Council says<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/2182217/smartwatches-and-fitness-bands-suunto-apple-and\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fhong-kong-economy%2Farticle%2F2182217%2Fsmartwatches-and-fitness-bands-suunto-apple-and&d=D1Y0%2Fdp%2BO8vcwf99EFFcLDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=575bc8d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/hong-kong-economy/article/2182217/smartwatches-and-fitness-bands-suunto-apple-and</a><br />\n<br />\n南早不只是重點報導大陸官方新聞，唱好中共政權，現已淪落到出切頭切尾content farm式假新聞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n消委會對運動手環熱量消耗偏差測試，眾所周知，小米手帶「小米Xiaomi Amazfit Bip」偏差達87%，連一卷衛生紙都有心跳86，震驚全城。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n南華早報 (SCMP) 這篇報導以Suunto, Apple, Garmin不準確起題，但令人驚訝的事，內文腳只寫一段：<br />\n<em>&quot;Three of the models tested had up to 88 per cent deviation when measuring the amount of calories burned walking, running or cycling.&quot;<br />\n</em><br />\n其中兩個小米樣本「小米Xiaomi Amazfit Bip」同「小米 Xiaomi Mi Band 3」  則完全無提及消委會的測試結果。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連關於大陸產品既新聞都要河蟹，香港的新聞自由真係凍過冰水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"799d7b79432faff71d5d2f6c9210b6df01927f45","tid":985325,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9aca3ba09d634654ed59fc7f48544924755456e","tid":985325,"uid":51937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09790868c11e5e10ff175598de78033f416ad92","tid":985325,"uid":28195,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"文章記者Zoe Low自稱台灣人，畢業LSE同台灣某大學，睇黎同大陸無關係，但暗地裡都係做content farm寫手"},{"pid":"0fa4da395222d984695b2a66a98b83c178353bf0","tid":985325,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:50:03.000Z","msg":"Red China Morning Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5524be6899ac5053f9ad05ab04b5b81f9aeb172","tid":985325,"uid":19501,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:54:49.000Z","msg":"紅底垃圾"},{"pid":"b33377cc3f37199a9ae252b047c491926fd84689","tid":985325,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:07:31.000Z","msg":"唔係第一次啦<br />\n<br />\n上次改大陸拼音 企圖掩飾垃圾既醜態"},{"pid":"6400e663e4738b6ac6768ed1d182e321e7bb3309","tid":985325,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"仲鳩過香港01份報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31e14dbc7eb160cbc7f3f4615bfa26d02789884","tid":985325,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"南早賣咗盤好耐啦<br />\n不用分得那麼細 小米阿里騰訊都係一擔擔"},{"pid":"6a4af18b6d1ef836e949b204c902a9e1458eec69","tid":985325,"uid":39550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:22:07.000Z","msg":"97後已經當SCMP唔存在"},{"pid":"de41bb39a25bfc195ad9297505f1504f30151e5c","tid":985325,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T08:28:05.000Z","msg":"zoe.low@scmp.com"},{"